  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nI would like push metrics to prometheus pushgateway using basic authentication.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nTwo new configuration fields to provide username and password or we can add it in the url https://user:pass@host:port/metric.\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nRemove authentication from pushgateway\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nPrometheus-net support it by using a custom http client https://github.com/prometheus-net/prometheus-net#publishing-to-pushgateway-with-basic-authentication\r\n",
